{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c95623d8a5","title":"对某些铁路不破坏或只作战术性破坏","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ab4f7f3d12","index":0,"year":1948,"month":1,"day":8,"articleId":"c95623d8a5"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d998630c73","type":"paragraph","text":"对某些铁路不破坏或只作战术性破坏","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c95623d8a5"},{"id":"b6a0ce45fd","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年1月8日）林、罗，并告中工委：东北与华北敌人意打少，几个月后形势将起变化。请考虑某些铁路不破坏或只作战术性破坏，而不彻底破坏。例如彰武、新立电、义州、承德间铁路不加破坏，打虎山，锦州、山海关、天津回铁路只作战术性破坏，铁岭、长春间及吉林、长春间铁路则不再破坏，沟帮子、营口、大石桥间及鞍山以南铁路似亦可不再破坏如何，望的办。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c95623d8a5"},{"id":"f58fa747d4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c95623d8a5"},{"id":"6119153c37","type":"paragraph","text":"子齐[1]林、罗，指林彪、罗荣想，当时分别任东北野我军司令员兼政治委员和副致治委员。2义州，旧州名，即辽宁义县。打虎山，即今大虎山，位于辽宁黑山县南部。31义州，旧州名，即辽宁义县。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c95623d8a5"}],"page":{"id":"04f85ba824","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c95623d8a5","start":498,"end":498}}}},"__N_SSG":true}